nd configurations for developing a microcontroller based solar tracking system; which will automatically control the motor position by tracking maximum light intensity with the help of Solar Tracking Sensor (designed and tested); and, displays the updated position of the motor in a 16x2 LCD display [11,<mark class="nova-legacy-e-text-highlight nova-legacy-e-text-highlight--color-yellow">12]</mark>. The required components list to configure and design the system is given in the Table I.  ...</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="nova-legacy-c-tooltip__arrow nova-legacy-c-tooltip__arrow nova-legacy-c-tooltip__arrow--body"><div class="nova-legacy-c-tooltip__arrow-tip"></div></div></div></div></div><div class="nova-legacy-o-stack__item"><div class="nova-legacy-v-citation-item__context-source"><div itemProp="citation" itemscope="" itemType="http://schema.org/ScholarlyArticle" class="nova-legacy-v-publication-item nova-legacy-v-publication-item--size-m gtm-figure-citation-item"><div class="nova-legacy-v-publication-item__body"><div class="nova-legacy-v-publication-item__stack nova-legacy-v-publication-item__stack--gutter-m"><div class="nova-legacy-v-publication-item__stack-item"><div class="nova-legacy-e-text nova-legacy-e-text--size-l nova-legacy-e-text--family-sans-serif nova-legacy-e-text--spacing-none nova-legacy-e-text--color-inherit nova-legacy-e-text--clamp-2 nova-legacy-v-publication-item__title" itemProp="headline"><a class="nova-legacy-e-link nova-legacy-e-link--color-inherit nova-legacy-e-link--theme-bare" href="publication/338939016_Design_of_an_Automatic_High_Precision_Solar_Tracking_System_with_an_Integrated_Solar_Sensor">Design of an Automatic High Precision Solar Tracking System with an Integrated Solar Sensor</a></div></div><div class="nova-legacy-v-publication-item__stack-item"><div class="nova-legacy-v-publication-item__meta"><div class="nova-legacy-v-publication-item__meta-left"><span class="nova-legacy-e-badge nova-legacy-e-badge-